-C SWORDD- Intermove sword demon
-C
-C Declarations
-C
-	SUBROUTINE SWORDD
-	IMPLICIT INTEGER (A-Z)
-	INCLUDE 'dparam.for'
-	LOGICAL INFEST,FINDXT
-C
